  "instructions": [
    "Preheat oven to 350°F (175°C).",
    "In a large bowl, mix together the malted cereal, chopped pistachios, and raisins.",
    "In a separate bowl, whisk together the Greek yogurt, honey, cinnamon, and salt.",
    "Add the sliced almonds, cocoa powder, and dried figs to the yogurt mixture and stir to combine.",
    "Pour the yogurt mixture over the cereal mixture and stir until well combined.",
    "If using, sprinkle bread crumbs on top and press gently into the mixture.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a baking dish and bake for 20 minutes, or until lightly toasted.",
    "Remove from the oven and let cool for 5 minutes before serving."
